$HR
d)  Complete the table for \( m(x) = \frac{g(x)}{f(x)} \)
$BCENTER
\{ begintable(7) \}
\{ row( "\( x \)" , @x ) \}
\{ row( "\( m(x) \)", ans_rule(8), ans_rule(8), ans_rule(8), ans_rule(8), ans_rule(8), ans_rule(8)  ) \}
\{ endtable() \}
